data.description: Welcome to this wonderful 4-bedroom, 2.5-bathroom family home located in the desirable Springtree Subdivision in Cibolo, stretching over 3372 sq ft on a spacious .44 acre corner lot. Drawing you in with great curb appeal, this home boasts a welcoming interior with formal living and dining areas catering to all your fine dining and entertainment needs. Taking center stage, the large family room sets a cozy ambiance for family bonding time, while the adjacent flex room offers the perfect space for a game room or additional entertainment area. Gourmet meals await in the island kitchen, featuring granite counters, a breakfast bar, bright white cabinetry, and a cozy dining area. French doors add a charming touch, leading to the back patio. Moving upstairs, you'll find a bonus room providing extra space for leisure or work. The primary ensuite is a personal retreat, boasting enough room for a sitting area, a large bathroom with dual vanities, a separate shower and soaking tub, and a spacious walk-in closet. The three additional bedrooms share a bath with dual vanities and a shower/tub combo, further enhancing the home's functionality and convenience. Outside, the covered patio overlooks the multi-level backyard, creating an ideal venue for open-air relaxation or entertaining guests. Located less than 1 mile from EVO & Santiko entertainment centers and conveniently near the Randolph AFB, this home promises a blend of comfort and accessibility.
